To initialize git repositary
git init(it will create .git file)
Hidden files/directories will start with '.(dot)'
To the git status- git status-
To create user name and email
git config --global user.name "User name"
git config --global user.email "email id"
To check user created -> git config --list
to update user details-> git config --global user.name "updated user name"
we can't create two users
Delete user -> git config --global --unset user.name and git config --global --unset user.email